<item>
 <title>China and the United States: Leading on Climate Action--New Challenges, New Opportunities</title>
 <link>http://www.chinafaqs.org/library/china-and-united-states-leading-climate-action-new-challenges-new-opportunities</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-filefield field-field-image&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
