<item>
 <title>Secretaries of Commerce and Energy to Lead Clean Energy Trade Mission to China</title>
 <link>http://www.chinafaqs.org/blog-posts/secretaries-commerce-and-energy-lead-clean-energy-trade-mission-china</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-filefield field-field-image&quot;&gt;
