<item>
 <title>6 ChinaFAQs Experts Testify Before the U.S.-China Economic and Security Review Commission</title>
 <link>http://www.chinafaqs.org/blog-posts/6-chinafaqs-experts-testify-us-china-economic-and-security-review-commission</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-filefield field-field-image&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
